// Plan:
// * Project each item to a prefix of its name
// * Create a second projection to a NDepCheck command usingthe same file, but "one ply deeper"

// Initial call: -dd LEFT (top) -dd INFILE inputfile
// e.g. src\NDepCheck\bin\Debug\NDepCheck.exe -dd LEFT a.b -dd RIGHT a.b.k.l -dd INFILE WSTestDep.dip -dd OUTFILE files\WSTestDep.html -ds c:\temp\InnerDrilldown.nd

-configure ProjectItems { -projection-list
    $ N(Name)      ---% NU(Name:Url)
    
    < (LEFT.*)     ---% \1:run?p00=-lz&p01=-dd%3dLEF%54&p02=\1&p03=-dd%3dRIGH%54&p04=RIGHT&p05=-dd%3dINFIL%45&p06=INFILE&p07=-dd%3dOUTFIL%45&p08=OUTFILE~\1~RIGHT.base&p09=-ds%3d..\scripts\InnerDrilldown.nd
		< (LEFT.*).**  ---% \1:run?p00=-lz&p01=-dd%3dLEF%54&p02=\1&p03=-dd%3dRIGH%54&p04=RIGHT&p05=-dd%3dINFIL%45&p06=INFILE&p07=-dd%3dOUTFIL%45&p08=OUTFILE~\1~RIGHT.base&p09=-ds%3d..\scripts\InnerDrilldown.nd
    > (RIGHT.*)    ---% \1:run?p00=-lz&p01=-dd%3dLEF%54&p02=LEFT&p03=-dd%3dRIGH%54&p04=\1&p05=-dd%3dINFIL%45&p06=INFILE&p07=-dd%3dOUTFIL%45&p08=OUTFILE~LEFT~\1.base&p09=-ds%3d..\scripts\InnerDrilldown.nd
		> (RIGHT.*).** ---% \1:run?p00=-lz&p01=-dd%3dLEF%54&p02=LEFT&p03=-dd%3dRIGH%54&p04=\1&p05=-dd%3dINFIL%45&p06=INFILE&p07=-dd%3dOUTFIL%45&p08=OUTFILE~LEFT~\1.base&p09=-ds%3d..\scripts\InnerDrilldown.nd
		! **         ---% :
}
INFILE
-transform ProjectItems

